<li id="cite_note-khoshnaw-24">^ <a href="#cite_ref-khoshnaw_24-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-khoshnaw_24-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.wscgames.com/cgi/player.cgi?given=Karl&amp;surname=Khoshnaw&amp;country=Germany&amp;exact=1" class="external text" title="http://www.wscgames.com/cgi/player.cgi?given=Karl&amp;surname=Khoshnaw&amp;country=Germany&amp;exact=1" rel="nofollow">"WSC Player Information: Karl Khoshnaw"</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.wscgames.com/cgi/player.cgi?given=Karl&amp;surname=Khoshnaw&amp;country=Germany&amp;exact=1" class="external free" title="http://www.wscgames.com/cgi/player.cgi?given=Karl&amp;surname=Khoshnaw&amp;country=Germany&amp;exact=1" rel="nofollow">http://www.wscgames.com/cgi/player.cgi?given=Karl&amp;surname=Khoshnaw&amp;country=Germany&amp;exact=1</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2006-04-27</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=WSC+Player+Information%3A+Karl+Khoshnaw&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wscgames.com%2Fcgi%2Fplayer.cgi%3Fgiven%3DKarl%26surname%3DKhoshnaw%26country%3DGermany%26exact%3D1&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Scrabble"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
