<li id="cite_note-26"><b><a href="#cite_ref-26" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.scrabulizer.com/blog/post/3" class="external text" title="http://www.scrabulizer.com/blog/post/3" rel="nofollow">Record for the Highest Scoring Scrabble Move</a> at scrabulizer.com</li>
