<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Scrabble&amp;action=edit&amp;section=32" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Mattel's <a href="http://www.mattelscrabble.com/en/adults/index.html" class="external text" title="http://www.mattelscrabble.com/en/adults/index.html" rel="nofollow">Scrabble website</a></li>
<li>Hasbro's <a href="http://www.hasbro.com/scrabble/home.cfm" class="external text" title="http://www.hasbro.com/scrabble/home.cfm" rel="nofollow">Scrabble website</a></li>
